title: The Beatles - Garage Tapes
description:
Track Listing (mp3):

1. If I Fell - (JOHN LENNON DEMOS: Recorded over fans tape message which was recorded on New Year&#039;s Eve 1963)

2. Don&#039;t Bother Me - (GEORGE HARRISON DEMO: Recorded in a hotel room in Bournemouth, August 1963. Guitar exercises added.)

3. McCartney Instrumentals- (Various Instrumentals Including: "Michelle"(Demo); "Three Coins in a Fountain"; "Rockin and Rollin" (John and Paul).)

4. Please Mr Postman (1 & 2) - (Two versions)

5. It Wont Be Long (1 & 2) - (Two versions)

6. Love Me Do - (Accoustic version)

7. Tammy Tell Me True - (John & Paul Singing)

8. The Bible Bit - (GERRY MARSDEN, JOHN LENNON & GEORGE HARRISON: Readings From The Bible)

9. RAGA - (From Unreleased APPLE FILM 1968.)
